Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,新月说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.97,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-B-GBK\fad(1000,0)\frz328.3\be1\fs30\pos(682.133,192.267)\1c\c&H00BC967F}月{\1c&H008BEDA1}亮{\1c&H006EFBE0}和{\1c&H006BC1EA}太{\1c&H006E8AE0}阳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳要醒了 我去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 素晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会到最后全部都记住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不是到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,最后还有下文
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是「月亮与太阳」第2话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 讲给我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天 太阳和新月决定出门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后新月说想早上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳说想晚上去
